**Jay** | Admin Investigative | Joke
__Basics__
Each night, Jay can check the role list and receive information.
__Details__
Once per game, Jay can say the name of any player and a role and that is automatically true. Jay cannot create another Admin.
They are immune to disguises and obstructions because what they say happens instead.
While Jay is alive ts can not win.
Jay wins when their chosen team (during day 0) does.
